      • onDisable

        void onDisable()

        NOTE: This will be callen if you set the enabled-status to true with setEnabled(boolean). Do not call this explicit!

      • onEnable

        Will be callen on disable.

        NOTE: This will be callen if you set the enabled-status to false with setEnabled(boolean). Do not call this explicit!

                    java.lang.Object obj)
        Registers the given command Class with the given Object. Will call CommandRegistrationUtil.registerCommands(Class, Object, org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin) with plugin as the root plugin.
        Parameters:
        clazz - The Class where the commands are located.
        obj - An Object of the given Class.
        See Also:
        CommandRegistrationUtil.registerCommands(java.lang.Class, java.lang.Object, org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin)
